com.fiu_CaSPR.Sajib.Intents

Class PostActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • com.fiu_CaSPR.Sajib.Intents.PostActivity

  • public class PostActivity
extends Activity
    Created by frankhu on 6/16/15. This Activity is meant to define the activity that should begin when the user has accessed the Facebook post page. We begin this activity so we can have complete control of what the user will post to Facebook; we utilize the temboo API in order to post to Facebook.
